---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Pricing — Mein Scope"
  description="Mein Scope pricing is quoted per clinic. Tell us about your setup and we'll follow up with a quote."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 pt-20 pb-16 text-center sm:pt-28">
    <span class="section-label">Pricing</span>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-ink-950 sm:text-5xl">
      Pricing, built around your clinic
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg text-ink-500 text-balance">
      Mein Scope doesn't have self-serve plans yet — we work directly with each clinic to
      understand your setup and quote accordingly.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="card">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink-950">Why we don't have a price list (yet)</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-ink-500">
        Mein Scope is early. We'd rather talk to a handful of clinics directly and get the product
        right than publish a price list before we've earned it. If you're evaluating Mein Scope,
        tell us a bit about your clinic — number of clinicians, procedure volume, single site or
        multiple — and we'll follow up with pricing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600">
          <Icon name="users" class="size-4" />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          A short conversation about how your clinic currently handles intake, capture, and
          reporting
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600">
          <Icon name="layout" class="size-4" />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          A live walkthrough of Mein Scope on a real or test device
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600">
          <Icon name="check-circle" class="size-4" />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          A pricing quote based on your setup — no obligation
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
        Talk to Us About Pricing
        <Icon name="arrow-right" class="size-4" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
